      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="23408802">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xingxuan/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u29084897-4.jpg" alt="浮游" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23408802/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23408802/" class="">第24页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xingxuan/" class=" " title="浮游">浮游</a>
                (这一刻的美丽，是极脆弱的东西)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="23408802">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">旧时人家堂上供奉有神主牌，牌上黑漆金字直书“某氏堂上高曾远祖之神位”，正是且字形状。祖宗无形可象，不得已用神主牌象征之。神主牌俗呼为“先人板板”，子孙后代不时燃香点蜡，跪拜致敬。

噗，原来“我日你先人板板”是这么来的</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-12-25 16:38</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>旧时人家堂上供奉有神主牌，牌上黑漆金字直书“某氏堂上高曾远祖之神位”，正是且字形状。祖宗无形可象，不得已用神主牌象征之。神主牌俗呼为“先人板板”，子孙后代不时燃香点蜡，跪拜致敬。</q></blockquote><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>噗，原来“我日你先人板板”是这么来的
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
